  "prompt": "What are the coolest IT companies in Chandigarh, India?",
  "response": "Chandigarh, known as a technology hub in India, is home to several innovative IT companies. Some of the most prominent and coolest IT companies in the region include:\n\n1. **Infosys**: As a major player in the global IT services sector, Infosys has a significant presence in Chandigarh, offering a range of IT solutions and consulting services.\n\n2. **Tech Mahindra**: With a focus on digital transformation and consulting, Tech Mahindra is a top choice for professionals seeking cutting-edge solutions in various industries.\n\n3. **Dell EMC**: Known for its contributions to IT hardware and solutions, Dell EMC operates a facility in the region, focusing on innovative storage and data management technologies.\n\n4. **Net Solutions**: A homegrown company, Net Solutions is recognized for its expertise in web and mobile development, as well as UX/UI design.\n\n5. **Kays Harbor Technologies**: Specializing in software consulting and product development, Kays Harbor offers services across healthcare, logistics, and retail sectors.\n\n6. **Spyglass**: Known for its advanced analytics and IoT (Internet of Things) solutions, Spyglass is a key player offering innovative approaches to data-driven business strategies.\n\n7. **IDS Infotech**: Offering services in software engineering, legal processing, and back-office operations, IDS Infotech is a well-regarded name in the IT sector.\n\n8. **TechBit Solutions**: A newer player in the field, TechBit is making waves with its focus on modern technological solutions and software development.\n\nThese companies combine innovative work cultures with cutting-edge technologies, making them attractive to professionals and clients alike. If you are exploring career opportunities or need IT services in Chandigarh, these companies can be a great starting point.",
